Arsenal have won seven straight games in the Premier League this season  . 
  Victory against Burnley will ensure the Gunners claim the longest winning streak in the top-flight this season . 
  Arsenal hold the record for the most consecutive wins - winning 14 games to clinch the title in 2002 . 
  Manchester City have also won seven games in a row  . 
  Arsenal are seven points behind leaders Chelsea . 
 